de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.examples.nar

Class Nar

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.examples.nar.Nar

  • public class Nar
extends Object
    An example Network Access Requestor. Requests handshakes at localhost:10229. The NAR uses a plain socket for testing, this cannot be used for production where TLS protection is mandatory. However to achieve TLS protection just us a Java SSL socket.
